**Purpose**: Data science portfolio project showcasing end-to-end ML lifecycle expertise

## Dataset Attribution

This project uses Amazon product review data for educational and portfolio demonstration purposes. The original dataset structure and format are based on publicly available Amazon review datasets commonly used in machine learning research and education.

